      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metrics (e.g., validation metric, E_val) must be computed and compared against application uncertainty; systematic bias must be identified and reported.",
      "rationale": "Area validation metric computed; mean hemolysis index prediction error is 18% across operating points. Systematic over-prediction at high shear rates identified. Achieved level 3 due to insufficient bias correction methodology."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
