      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must be conducted on a geometry and at operating conditions sufficiently similar to the COU device to support extrapolation; similarity gaps must be quantified.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic pump geometry used for validation differs from the proprietary VAD impeller in blade angle and gap width. Geometric similarity score estimated at 0.72; extrapolation uncertainty not fully propagated. Achieved level 3."
