      "acceptanceCriteria": "Blood analog fluid or bovine blood used in experiments must be characterized for relevant rheological properties; sample provenance and preparation protocol must be documented.",
      "rationale": "Bovine blood from single supplier used in FDA pump experiments. Hematocrit controlled to 33±2%. No inter-lot variability study performed. Sample preparation SOP referenced but not fully reproduced in submission. Achieved level 2."
