    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concludes that the simulation package is Accepted for the stated COU. The majority of assessed factors demonstrate sufficient evidence to support the hemolysis prediction decision, and Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification has been performed across all five operating points. Residual gaps in individual factor levels are judged to be within acceptable bounds given the conservative nature of the hemolysis model and the supporting experimental dataset.",
